Path: Nushell
Content:
blindFS 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14805] fixed PWD env_var for LSP
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14802] added inlay hints of variable types and command params for LSP
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14789] fixed unknown span for special variables 
``$in/$it``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14770] added document_symbols and workspace_symbols for LSP
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14742] implemented use of lsp-textdocument to handle utf16 position for LSP
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14798] made 
``table``
 only check for 
``use_ansi_coloring``
 config value
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14797] added 
``"whereis"``
 and 
``"get-command"``
 to 
``which``
 search terms
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14679] handled permission denied error at 
``nu_engine::glob_from``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14795] upgraded to Rust version 1.82
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14772] fixed 
``stor reset``
 when there are foreign keys
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14698] improved closure serialization
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14785] removed file accidentally re-introduced by merge
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14766] fixed extra newline on empty lists when $env.config.table.show_empty is set
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14758] added newline to empty list output
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14757] changed 
``PipelineData::into_value``
 to use internal 
``Value``
's span before passed in span
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14756] fixed config reset to use scaffold config files
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14755] prevented ndots expansion if prefixed with 
``./``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14750] added doccomments to 
``find``
 functions in EngineState and StateWorkingSet
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14749] added flag to 
``debug profile``
 to output duration field as Value::Duration
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14741] added run-time type checking for command pipeline input
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14782] updated typos workflow to 
``1.29.4``
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14773] enabled conditional 
``source``
 and 
``use``
 patterns by allowing 
``null``
 as a no-op module
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14763] made small, backwards compatible enhancements to std
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14687] fixed nuon conversions of range values
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14764] converted Path to 
``list``
 in main and preserved case
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14726] removed deprecated commands
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14803] prevented release workflow from triggering on nightly tags
dead10ck 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14760] expanded custom values on table display
userwiths 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14747] fixed root directory traversal issue
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14738] made custom completions inherit case_sensitive option from $env.config
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14708] prevented auto cd from canonicalizing symbolic path
Chen1Plus 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14699] fixed wrong error message of 
``save``
 command on Windows
ChetanXpro 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14592] fixed handling of zero-size cursor in binary viewer for explore command
